    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876990/extras/64a7684d426aa25914cf527b8719bb26.avif?t=1716564721\" width=614 height=346 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876990/extras/ec5da9799be318d66074fb9bf165bd79.webp?t=1716564721\" width=620 height=52 /></span><br>这里永远无条件欢迎那些被迫离开原部落的受伤和被遗弃的村民，这就可以很容易理解为什么老鼠的许多追随者愿意将他们的生命，有时甚至是他们的死亡，奉献给了这个部落。<br><br>这个部落没有时间举行宴会，甚至没有房子提供舒适的睡眠，只有努力工作才值得庆祝，但如果你有足够的精力来庆祝，那么你当然可以庆祝，不过之后应该更加努力工作才行......<br><br>这个部落为获得自己想要的东西以及生存会不知疲倦地工作和战斗。<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876990/extras/a13096cc81689c50ab151aa632f96535.webp?t=1716564721\" width=620 height=52 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876990/extras/0f95129a625ffa4d982de3b032c00e89.avif?t=1716564721\" width=614 height=664 /></span><br><br>艾尔是强大的萨满和无情的战士，她用铁腕般方式领导着老鼠部落。她为其部落传授了萨满们的方式，以保证即使在负伤严重的情况下也能存活下去，并确保他们的敌人不会。<br><br>有些人甚至说，她对黑暗实践的掌握，甚至到了能让死去的野兽从赫尔海姆的深处复活的程度……<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876990/extras/a4e9ffcd3df3923d4843251a542693ef.webp?t=1716564721\" width=620 height=52 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876990/extras/ec0f587ec6f6364f64d65c0cfa698454.poster.avif?t=1716564721\" width=614 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876990/extras/ec0f587ec6f6364f64d65c0cfa698454.webm?t=1716564721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876990/extras/ec0f587ec6f6364f64d65c0cfa698454.mp4?t=1716564721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>通过艾尔的训练，该部族可以训练萨满，这些强大的部队在激烈的战斗中无畏地战斗，并在战斗结束后照顾伤员。他们同时也会为同盟伸出援手并为他们治疗。<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876990/extras/a6b3f2ffbafe6509b8a7687643e516e3.webp?t=1716564721\" width=620 height=52 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 部落里有更多的村民，但他们都负伤了。负伤单位不计入幸福度要求。<br></li><li>该部落无法进入房屋，但所有非神秘建筑都提供住房。一旦达到最大的人口，额外的村民将被置放在人口储备。<br></li><li>萨满营取代了治疗小屋，训练萨满，使其即使是在你的领地之外也能够战斗并治疗多个单位和同盟。<br></li><li>当部落单位杀死敌人或死亡时，尸体将在萨满营进行火化，产生知识并更快吸引新村民。<br></li><li>过度劳动取代宴会，并以牺牲工人的生命为代价来提升所有生产量。</li></ul><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876990/extras/d83a8d78981a1581d865ab3afc75ee2f.webp?t=1716564721\" width=620 height=52 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>声望200</strong><br>当被艾尔疗愈时，你的军队消耗的食物减少50%。</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>[b声望500[/b]<br>人口储备最多可容纳+4个村民。净化柴堆的最大持续时间延长至6个月。</li></ul><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876990/extras/fd55e559fc5991cd2bda31e82e54d110.webp?t=1716564721\" width=620 height=52 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>入伍</strong><br>负伤的单位训练成为军队的-50%克朗花费。<br><br></li><li><strong>过度拥挤</strong><br>你可以在一个区域中放置两个相同类型的建筑，除了防御塔。<br><br></li><li><strong>入侵</strong><br>当你杀死中立派系的单位时，你可以获得一些他们最喜欢的交易资源。中立派系的建筑可以容纳额外的人口。<br><br></li><li><strong>疼痛抑制</strong><br>负伤单位的移动和攻击速度提升30%。<br><br></li><li><strong>血缘关系</strong><br>艾尔可以牺牲她的部分生命来在接下来的5秒钟内治疗你在区域内的所有单位。</li></ul><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876990/extras/c2b103fd0335f77629b021586d037f3b.webp?t=1716564721\" width=620 height=52 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876990/extras/ca0cdada6b33504dddd9a8156260d502.poster.avif?t=1716564721\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876990/extras/ca0cdada6b33504dddd9a8156260d502.webm?t=1716564721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876990/extras/ca0cdada6b33504dddd9a8156260d502.mp4?t=1716564721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>可以在萨满营召唤加姆的化身。",
